  <h1 style="font-family:'Raleway'; font-size: 2.5em"><font color="#2D28B5"><b>RevBayes</b></font></h1>
  <h3>Bayesian phylogenetic inference using probabilistic graphical models and an interpreted language</h3>
</div>
